p.seg:
With these witnesses : John, archdeacon of Durham; Alan, priest of Wallsend;
                  Master Thomas; Andrew, archdeacon of Lothian; Master Richard
                  of Coldingham; Patrick, dean; Hervé and Romfar, priests;
                  Master Thomas of Lamberton; Richard, archdeacon’s chaplain;
                  Richard, parson of Tweedmouth; Richard, son of Hervé; Walter
                  the seneschal; Adam of Wallsend; Elias of Wallsend; and many
                  others.
